SELECT u.name, w.workout_name, e.exercise_name FROM user_profiles u INNER JOIN user_workouts uw ON u.id = uw.user_id INNER JOIN workouts w ON w.id = uw.workout_id INNER JOIN exercises e ON e.id = uw.exercise_id;

SELECT u.name, w.workout_name, e.exercise_name, uw.sets, uw.reps, uw.weight FROM user_profiles u INNER JOIN user_workouts uw ON u.id = uw.user_id INNER JOIN workouts w ON w.id = uw.workout_id INNER JOIN exercises e ON e.id = uw.exercise_id WHERE uw.sets >= 4 AND uw.reps <= 12 AND uw.weight > 25.0 ORDER BY u.name ASC, w.workout_name ASC, e.exercise_name ASC;
